#: /16x9/Custom_1107_DialogConfirmFactoryReset.xml
msgctxt "#31467"
msgid "Welcome to Madnox! For the best experience, we recommend applying the default settings. This will configure all visual options and features. Would you like to apply the Madnox recommended settings now?"
msgstr "Merħba f'Madnox! Għall-aħjar esperjenza, nirrakkomandaw li tapplika s-settings default. Dan se jikkonfigura l-għażliet u l-karatteristiċi viżwali kollha. Tixtieq tapplika s-settings rakkomandati minn Madnox issa?"

#: /16x9/Custom_1107_DialogConfirmFactoryReset.xml
msgctxt "#31468"
msgid "This will restore all skin settings to their original defaults.[CR][CR]Your current customizations will be lost.[CR]Are you sure you want to continue?"
msgstr "Dan se jirrestawra s-settings kollha tal-ġilda għad-defaults oriġinali tagħhom.[CR][CR]Il-personalizzazzjonijiet attwali tiegħek se jintilfu.[CR]Żgur li trid tkompli?"

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31470"
msgid "Restore Madnox skin settings to day 1 out of the box startup values. Only affects skin settings, does not alter or change anything else like scripts or plugins."
msgstr "Irrestawra s-settings tal-ġilda Madnox għall-valuri tal-ewwel jum tal-istartjar. Jaffettwa biss is-settings tal-ġilda, ma jbiddilx jew ma jbiddel xejn ieħor bħal scripts u plugins."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31471"
msgid "Allows customization of default media flags without requiring outside hacks to the skin. This allows you to custom select which video container icons will be displayed for WebDL, 1080p, 720p etc. This can be reset at any time."
msgstr "Jippermetti l-personalizzazzjoni tal-bnadar tal-midja default mingħajr ma jkun hemm bżonn ta' hacks esterni fuq il-ġilda. Dan jippermettilek tagħżel personalment liema ikoni tal-kontenituri tal-vidjo se jintwerew għal WebDL, 1080p, 720p eċċ. Dan jista' jiġi rrisettjat fi kwalunkwe ħin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31472"
msgid "Enables setting of the color of \"In-Progress\" bar feature."
msgstr "Jattiva l-issettjar tal-kulur tal-karatteristika tal-bar \"In-Progress\"."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Sets of the color of \"In-Progress\" bar feature globally when enabled."
msgstr "Jissettja l-kulur tal-karatteristika tal-bar \"In-Progress\" globalment meta tkun attivata."

