#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Current built-in revision level of the default Madnox values to reset / initialize the skin."
msgstr "Il-livell ta' reviżjoni kurrenti integrat tal-valuri default ta' Madnox biex tirrisettja / tinizjalizza l-ġilda."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31507"
msgid "Select if an intro video will play when Kodi is first started. None: No video, Built-In: Kodi's release level intro video, Custom: Pick video of your choice to display."
msgstr "Agħżel jekk vidjo tal-intro hux se jindaqq meta Kodi jinbeda l-ewwel darba. L-ebda: L-ebda vidjo, Integrat: Il-vidjo tal-intro tal-livell tal-verżjoni ta' Kodi, Personalizzat: Agħżel vidjo tal-għażla tiegħek biex jintwera."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31508"
msgid "This setting forces the media flag to resolution flag as 4K or 2160p providing user icon control without skin modifcations."
msgstr "Dan is-setting iġiegħel lill-bandiera tal-midja turi bħala bandiera tar-riżoluzzjoni 4K u 2160p, li jipprovdi kontroll tal-ikona tal-utent mingħajr modifiki fil-ġilda."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31509"
msgid "Change the stars color displayed in the video info line. Click to cycle through fixed colors or select a custom color."
msgstr "Ibdel il-kulur tal-istilel murija fil-linja tal-informazzjoni tal-vidjo. Ikklikkja biex iddur bejn kuluri fissi jew agħżel kulur personalizzat."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31510"
msgid "Allows star ratings style to use a custom color when it is set to \"Custom\"."
msgstr "Jippermetti li l-istil tal-klassifikazzjoni tal-istilel juża kulur personalizzat meta jkun issettjat bħala \"Personalizzat\"."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Dedicated addon for Madnox required for Piers+. Moves all free running scripts to a dedicated addon for security purposes."
msgstr "Addon dedikat għal Madnox meħtieġ għal Piers+. Iċaqlaq l-iscripts kollha li jaħdmu waħedhom lejn addon dedikat għal skopijiet ta' sigurtà."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "TMDbHelper provides several tools to assist skinners with retrieving information from TMDb, OMDb and Trakt APIs."
msgstr "TMDbHelper jipprovdi diversi għodod biex jgħin lill-iżviluppaturi tal-ġilda jiksbu informazzjoni minn TMDb, OMDb u APIs ta' Trakt."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31513"
msgid "Wikipedia addon for Kodi."
msgstr "Addon tal-Wikipedia għal Kodi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31514"
msgid "Advanced CinemaVision replacement that can be enabled to replace Madnox's built in simpler CinemaMode. Allows the ultimate CinemaMode experience and customisation."
msgstr "Sostituzzjoni avvanzata ta' CinemaVision li tista' tiġi attivata biex tissostitwixxi l-CinemaMode integrat u aktar sempliċi ta' Madnox. Jippermetti l-aqwa esperjenza u personalizzazzjoni ta' CinemaMode."

#: /16x9/Includes_CustomSelect.xml
