msgid "Optional extras installer"
msgstr "Installatur tal-extras fakultattivi"

#: Custom_1109_DialogConfirmExtrasInstall.xml
msgctxt "#31520"
msgid "This will re-run the optional extras installer. All extras will be downloaded and installed in a disabled state. Enable only what you need in Settings > Skin Settings > Addons."
msgstr "Dan se jerġa' jħaddem l-installatur tal-extras fakultattivi. L-extras kollha se jitniżżlu u jiġu installati fi stat diżattivat. Attiva biss dak li għandek bżonn f'Settings > Settings tal-Ġilda > Addons."

